# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# TOP SARKARI JOBS — _redirects (Netlify / Cloudflare Pages)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Fixes:
#   ✅ WWW non-WWW duplicate (enforce www)
#   ✅ Old ?section= → clean /section/<slug>/ URLs (301 permanent)
#   ✅ Old ?url= tool URLs → noindex + serve view.html
#   ✅ /jobs/<slug>/ → job.html (200 rewrite, no redirect)
#   ✅ /section/<slug>/ → view.html (200 rewrite, SEO-friendly)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── 1. Enforce WWW (non-www → www) ───────────────────────────────
# NOTE: This works on Netlify. For GitHub Pages, set CNAME to www
# and redirect non-www at DNS level (Cloudflare: Redirect Rule)
# https://topsarkarijobs.com/*  https://www.topsarkarijobs.com/:splat  301!

# ── 2. Clean /section/<slug>/ → view.html (200 rewrite) ─────────
# Googlebot indexes /section/latest-jobs/ as the canonical page
/section/*    /view.html    200

# ── 3. Job detail clean URLs → job handler (200 rewrite) ────────
/jobs/*       /job.html     200

# ── 4. Category clean URLs ──────────────────────────────────────
/category/*   /category.html  200

# ── 5. State job listing clean URLs /state/<name>/ ──────────────
/state/        /state-jobs.html  200
/state/*       /state-jobs.html  200

# ── 6. Search ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/search/*     /search.html  200

