# ── 10. 404 fallback ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTE: Do NOT add "/* /404.html 404" here!
# Netlify/Cloudflare Pages automatically serves 404.html for unmatched routes.
# An explicit /* rule intercepts ALL requests — including real files like
# job.html, state-jobs.html, index.html — breaking the entire site.
# Just place 404.html in the root and let the CDN handle it automatically.
